{"tid":364093,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講 年青人以家仲可以點","createTime":"2017-08-18T06:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T07:31:20.000Z","uid":132030,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8cb104c3543ffc24d45e786bfad69e1ca21f695","tid":364093,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:04:56.000Z","msg":"雨傘革命可以令到咁多人出黎<br />\n係香港最大型ge 一次革命<br />\n但結果最後咩都爭取唔到<br />\n政府仲變本加厲<br />\n全部狗官爭住繼續向中央刷鞋<br />\n愈來愈撚衰<br />\n以家仲要判佢地坐監<br />\n年青人敢企出黎嘅勇氣將會更加小<br />\n我地仲可以做d咩 我睇到嘅只係只可以等死<br />\n就算成功再一次大型革命 <br />\n結果其實都係一樣<br />\n我以經睇唔到任何野可以阻止到暴政"},{"pid":"4d5fcf31b7413c8d5fea9fed901f8b5c9c81b841","tid":364093,"uid":74402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:06:45.000Z","msg":"鬥長命"},{"pid":"d3fac47adcc93763024e2a06d1df9dd0138054f1","tid":364093,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:06:52.000Z","msg":"搵錢"},{"pid":"feb91e4f36b6a21a4fa5561d760faa9582760c1e","tid":364093,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:08:33.000Z","msg":"佔中並不是革命"},{"pid":"39a57b1e2b2202e1d946d9fd082b03b689d2f1d3","tid":364093,"uid":6352,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬥長命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同，現時韜光養晦係最合理做法"},{"pid":"ad6cbfde559d6ee6c7507c96971e381f2d61c64a","tid":364093,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:11:58.000Z","msg":"我諗年青人係想改變<br />\n不過爭取改變而導致坐監<br />\n好多人都唔會有咁嘅心理準備"},{"pid":"272e49c1f2752a691aa3bf4b6bd9cc92c8f170ba","tid":364093,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佔中並不是革命</blockquote><br />\n咁係咩？"},{"pid":"5f1150a66fda13082f8a80ea672737c91e388f33","tid":364093,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鬥長命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同，現時韜光養晦係最合理做法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger"},{"pid":"a9c9aee9da59d3a284b702724eee196f14275a44","tid":364093,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佔中並不是革命</blockquote><br />\n咁係咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係運動。革命係會死人的"},{"pid":"16db503aee471d1214a6327e478270f62f3e6102","tid":364093,"uid":74402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鬥長命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同，現時韜光養晦係最合理做法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n年青人要去參選一切有話語權既位置<br />\n不單指議員，更可以參選大廈法團，公屋互委會，學校校董會等等<br />\n<br />\n當土共殺埋身時，無謂再硬碰搞到自己坐監<br />\n但一定唔可以唔出聲"},{"pid":"181eb153f4e4c5858c9790e3582007e1eba2ff54","tid":364093,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鬥長命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同，現時韜光養晦係最合理做法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger</blockquote><br />\n鬥長命有咩用阿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fb6ce9f3694b8f9e9c59d5d32bbb11e1a4a53a","tid":364093,"uid":91191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:19:46.000Z","msg":"啱呀鬥長命<br />\n等到中共倒台<br />\n香港先有出頭天<br />\n不過都無人知到時係咪會有第一個老共出黎玩<br />\n及時行樂啦"},{"pid":"e72ecb92c10d051ce3d904bbbf70de06eee7d523","tid":364093,"uid":42687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鬥長命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同，現時韜光養晦係最合理做法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n年青人要去參選一切有話語權既位置<br />\n不單指議員，更可以參選大廈法團，公屋互委會，學校校董會等等<br />\n<br />\n當土共殺埋身時，無謂再硬碰搞到自己坐監<br />\n但一定唔可以唔出聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger,. 慢慢入侵，再等班老野死哂先有希望"},{"pid":"2e8ba0ca1f4109016fa572c6e56696f385c2dd48","tid":364093,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:22:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱呀鬥長命<br />\n等到中共倒台<br />\n香港先有出頭天<br />\n不過都無人知到時係咪會有第一個老共出黎玩<br />\n及時行樂啦</blockquote><br />\n屌 咁即係選擇坐以待斃無分別"},{"pid":"da78680899741eea21a6cde891f04e2e74c86771","tid":364093,"uid":74402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鬥長命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同，現時韜光養晦係最合理做法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger</blockquote><br />\n鬥長命有咩用阿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家係有班on9諗住一步登天可以推翻政府<br />\n唔係話唔得，但你有冇咁大政治能量去號召市民支持你先？<br />\n強大如梁天琦、黃之峰今時今刻都要收皮<br />\n仲有邊個有咁大政治能量反抗？<br />\n無既就要儲政治能量，<br />\n未必需要政治明星，<br />\n一班有社會身份既人肯反抗好過得一個所謂明星反抗"},{"pid":"e57008666ac193abb2971db7cc5798904c325e9e","tid":364093,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"其實點解仲講我地係對抗政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本由一開始對既就係 共產黨<br />\n<br />\n一個連美國 俄羅斯都驚既政權呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好再用政府黎做目標啦 各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad62a13a18f6c40c5f23df0ce6550bf8c453a24","tid":364093,"uid":74402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解仲講我地係對抗政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face